{"id":587656,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/【立此存照】享誉全世界的媒体第一次走进玉狗梁/","date":"2018-06-26T09:17:12Z","modified":"2018-06-26T09:17:12Z","title":"【立此存照】享誉全世界的媒体第一次走进玉狗梁","content":"<p><strong>来源： 有一个地方叫玉狗梁  作者卢文震（玉狗梁第一书记）</strong></p>\n<p>2018年的6月20日，玉狗梁又一个划时代意义的日子，美国 《纽约时报》记者要来玉狗梁的消息很快传遍了大街小巷。今天村里的家家户户早饭都比往常早了些，就连村里最年长的老人、91岁的杨素花、90岁的张荣花，还有几位八十多岁的老人也都吃完饭就早早的来到了村委会，都迫不及待的想看看享誉全世界的媒体记者究竟长啥样子。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587657\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587658\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁2.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁2-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>记者黄瑞黎、陈怡和摄影师看到这么多老人在迎接她他们，非常的高兴，愉快的跟大家一起合影。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁3.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587659\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁3-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁4.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587660\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁4.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁4-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁4-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁4-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>第一次来玉狗梁村采访的《纽约时报》记者是来自新加坡籍的驻北京记者 黄瑞黎Sui-lee Wee，中国的陈怡 ，中国香港的摄影师林亦非Lam Yik Fei ，她(他)们到达玉狗梁后，就立刻投入到采访中，展示出了世界知名媒体的工作态度和工作效率。（采访玉狗梁第一书记卢文震）</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁8.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587661\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁8.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁8-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁8-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁8-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>采访人称三姐的张志美</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁9.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587662\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁9.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁9-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁9-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁9-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁10.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587663\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁10.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁10-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁10-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁10-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁11.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587664\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁11.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁11-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁11-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁11-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁11-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>采访王占山、张喜英老两口时，张喜英大婶将家中新买的、具有坝上妇女服饰特色的头巾为记者亲自带上，能看得出，记者黄瑞黎、陈怡和摄影师林亦非是非常的开心。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁12.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587665\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁12.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁12-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁12-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁12-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>记者在拍摄村民家中墙上的老照片</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁13.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587666\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁13.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁13-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁13-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁13-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>采访许富、武启莲老两口</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_587667\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁14.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-587667\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁14.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁14-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁14-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁14-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁14-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">采访张志海、戈录云夫妻</p></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁15.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587668\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁15.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁15.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁15-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁15-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁15-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁16.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587669\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁16.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁16.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁16-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁16-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁16-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>县委宣传部常务副部长杜永库、两面井乡党委宣传委员 李春玲 陪同记者到荆万山、李翠花家中采访。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁17.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587670\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁17.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁17.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁17-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁17-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁17-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁17-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>采访妇女主任靳秀英结束后，靳秀英还向记者赠送了她自己设计的玉狗梁瑜伽剪纸，这可是纯手工、绝版、第一次赠送客人的玉狗梁瑜伽剪纸。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁18.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587671\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁18.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁18-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁18-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁18-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁19.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587672\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁19.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁19.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁19-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁19-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁19-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>记者黄瑞黎、陈怡晚上住在了靳秀英家，还亲自体验了一次烧火拉风箱和传统老火炕的感觉。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁20.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587673\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁20.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁20-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁20-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁20-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁20-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁21.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587674\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁21.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁21-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁21-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁21-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁21-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁22.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587675\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁22.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁22.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁22-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁22-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁22-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁22-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>记者黄瑞黎和陈怡采访中的瞬间</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁23.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587676\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁23.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁23.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁23-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁23-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁23-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁23-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>已经是夜里十点了，记者还在采访。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁24.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587677\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁24.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁24.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁24-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁24-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁24-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁24-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>记者黄瑞黎拍摄看到玉狗梁村民家家户户都挂着以习近平总书记为核心的党中央领导集体照片，忍不住拿起手机拍了下来。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁25.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587678\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁25.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁25.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁25-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁25-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁25-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁25-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁26.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587679\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁26.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁26.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁26-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁26-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁26-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁26-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>《纽约时报》的记者来到玉狗梁，是玉狗梁村历史上第一个外国媒体，而且是世界顶级的媒体到村里采访，村民们一致同意集体为《纽约时报》的记者们挂彩头，以表达全体村民对《纽约时报》和记者黄瑞黎、陈怡、摄影师林亦非的祝福。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁27.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587680\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁27.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁27.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁27-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁27-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁27-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁27-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>老人们第一次看无人机航拍中的自己</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁28.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587681\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁28.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁28.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁28-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁28-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁28-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁28-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>记者黄瑞黎、陈怡与玉狗梁村党支部书记、村委会主任张海，妇女主任、玉狗梁瑜伽带头人靳秀英和驻村第一书记卢文震合影</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁29.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587682\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁29.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁29.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁29-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁29-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁29-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>记者与瑜伽展示的村民们合影</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁30.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587683\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁30.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁30.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁30-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁30-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁30-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>在村民家中体验玉狗梁的莜面、土豆的间隙，抓紧时间采访了跟踪拍摄玉狗梁一年多的张家口市摄影家协会副主席赵占南，并告诉赵占南主席，玉狗梁村民们的热情好客和淳朴让她们非常感动，老人们的瑜伽精神更是让她们称赞，感谢赵主席向世人介绍了玉狗梁。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁31.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587684\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁31.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"386\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁31.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁31-300x211.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁31-768x539.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/玉狗梁31-1024x719.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>县委常委、宣传部长霍满明在采访结束后与记者进行了座谈，介绍了县委、县政府对玉狗梁瑜伽健身扶贫模式的大力支持与对玉狗梁整体发展的规划设想，代表张北县委、县政府感谢《纽约时报》驻北京记者站对玉狗梁瑜伽健身扶贫、以及张北县精准扶贫工作的关注与报道。（右三为县委常委、宣传部长霍满明、永库右一为常务副部长杜）</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2018/06/24/business/china-yoga-elderly-village.html\">nytimes | In a Chinese Village, Elderly Farmers Are Now Yogis</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hebgcdy.com/gd/system/2018/06/26/030332507.shtml\">河北日报 | 张家口在基层党组织推广“新时代讲习所”</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://zhangbei.hebnews.cn/2018-06/15/content_6920476.htm\">河北新闻网 | 张北县“新时代农民讲习所”开讲了</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.zjk139.com/zjk/xianqu/201803/177783.html\">张家口新闻网 | 玉狗梁乡村瑜伽荣登纪录电影《厉害了，我的国》</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.sohu.com/a/234591635_482902\">搜狐 | 厉害了！玉狗梁瑜伽村走向世界，爷爷奶奶放牛做饭都练瑜伽</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://feed.baidu.com/feed/data/wise/landingpage?s_type=news&amp;dsp=wise&amp;nid=1760502328317295504&amp;n_type=&amp;p_from=4\">百度 | 国级贫困村以瑜伽扶贫 全村能做“全莲花坐”</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[32609,35038,20377,9540,35039,9000,35037,35041,35042,35044,35043,35040,10076,35036]}